Class Weapon

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.server.cards.Card
      • it.polimi.se2019.server.cards.weapons.Weapon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Targetable, java.io.Serializable

    public class Weapon
extends Card
    A weapon is a card that has a few more functionality, in particular if can be loaded, it has a cost tobe reload and to get it. And can have some optional action units.
